itemDescription: Bishop of Wellington; British Anglican colonial bishop

wikipedia_page.main: Frederic Wallis (1854 – 24 June 1928) was an eminent Anglican priest.

response: In the churchyard is a memorial to Frederic Wallis, Bishop of Wellington, New Zealand, who married into the Williams family. It is made from the wood of a tree sent specially from New Zealand.
